latestPosts.caption:
Look who made it to @forbesindia 🥹

Getting featured in India’s Top 100 Digital Stars is one of my biggest achievements so far in my career. Always manifested being in Forbes 30 under 30 but to be featured in this form is a big accomplishment for my profession. 
Also a proud South Indian represent ❤️

I’m happy but I’m numb, I’m excited but also anxious. A lot of mixed feelings going on. Just Smiling ear to ear since I saw this. 🥰🥹
.
Got to share this moment with @hashithaak and VK. My biggest cheerleaders!! They have always been my loudesttt supporters and I couldn’t be here without them. From buying makeup for me in whatever little money my sister had to getting me my first camera she always always had my back and again I wouldn’t be here if not for her. 🫶🏻
This is a big winnn. 💃💃

Special mention to @shlaghagupta for keeping up with me, my patience, my tantrums, always having my back. Fighting with everyone for all my reasonable and unreasonable demands and sometimes being nice to me. More to goo 👀 
And @chtrbox @kritikathreen To 5 years 🥂 
.
.
#akankshakommirelly #forbes #forbesindia
